Package: shinypayload
Type: Package
Title: Accept POST Data and URL Parameters in Shiny (Same-Port Integration)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Pawan Rama", "Mali", email = "prm@outlook.in", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Handle POST requests on a custom path (e.g., /ingress) inside the same Shiny HTTP server using ui(req) + httpResponse. Expose latest payload as a reactive and provide helpers for query parameters.
